QuestData.Title: Whispers in the Darkness
QuestData.Description: If you don't mind, I'm trying VERY hard to prevent all of our worlds from collapsing into the void, AGAIN.$B$BOh, right, you helped me last time, didn't you? Well, you've got great timing. I'm in need of another Gate-Key.$B$BWell? Go on! The infinite horrors of the abyss aren't just going to wait until you've had a nap! Having that many tentacles makes them really antsy.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find a Void-Gate Key in the Shadowmoon Burial Grounds.
